- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as capsule networks have been used in computer vision tasks.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as deep learning is a subfield of AI.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but could be relevant as the paper discusses programming techniques for deep learning models.
